@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jzuocm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos((v1 - wp.abs(v2 + 0.97)))
    v0 = wp.sin(v1)
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin((v0 + 0.30 + v0 + 0.95)))
    v0 = (tmp / wp.exp((v2 + 0.80 * v2 + 0.68)))
    v1 = v1
    v1 = (0.91 + wp.cos((v0 + 0.97 / v2 + 0.62)))
    tmp = wp.cos((0.55 * (tmp + 0.90 / v2 + 0.70)))
    tmp = wp.exp((0.96 + (v1 + 0.16 + v1 + 0.79)))
    data[tid] = v0
